data.description: Welcome to Chambers Creek Terrace, a beautiful community of 8 townhome style condos along Chambers Creek! Enjoy the sounds of the bubbling creek from the paver patio of your HOA maintained park like rear yard! Single story living, open living/dining/kitchen plan. Living room features large slider glass door & window to soak in the views & wood burning fireplace w/insert. Spacious kitchen, updated cabinets, granite counters, stainless appliances & breakfast nook space. Formal dining room will easily accommodate a 6-8 seat table. Large primary bedroom w/ensuite bath & views of yard & creek. Second bedroom & full bath. 2 car detached garage. Private community bordering the South Puget Sound Wildlife Area. Come see this creek front home today!
